snippet.title: Darkest Dungeon - Terror and Madness Trailer (OFFICIAL)
snippet.description:
PRE-ORDER NOW and support the devs:
http://www.darkestdungeon.com/buy

Terror and madness in the cavernous depths. Official reveal trailer for Darkest Dungeon, an uncompromising RPG about the true cost of adventuring. Coming 2015 from Red Hook Studios. http://www.darkestdungeon.com
